<p>Dave&rsquo;s at WWDC, John&rsquo;s back holding down the fort, and your two geeks dive right in answering your questions and solving your problems. Topics include OS X Lion (no more &ldquo;Mac&rdquo; in that name!), File Vault 2, dual-booting your Mac, Bluetooth, Time Machine, migration, and more! Subscribe to this (it&rsquo;s free), download, press play, and enjoy!</p>
